# Project Conventions

- This is a React + TypeScript + Vite project using Trimble Modus Web Components
- Use `@trimble-oss/moduswebcomponents-react` for all UI components
- Follow Modus design system tokens for colors, spacing, and typography
- Keep components small and focused — extract logic into custom hooks
- Prefer named exports over default exports
